  "title": "Chinese Speech and Drama Teacher (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><u><strong>Summary</strong></u>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct Chinese and Drama lessons for pre-school/primary school children</li>\n  <li>Prepare students for performances, e.g. recitation, drama, sing and dance</li>\n  <li>Provide engaging and high-quality learning experiences in class children</li>\n  <li>Communicate with parents and provide constructive feedback in line with program requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Enjoys working with children and has minimum 1 year experience in</li>\n  <li>teaching Speech and Drama to preschool students.</li>\n  <li>Energetic, creative, passionate, good team player.</li>\n  <li>Has good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Relevant diploma or degree or any other professional teaching quaifications in Drama, Performance or Theatre will be considered</li>\n  <li>Acceptable to work across the island</li>\n</ul>",
